    "description": "Shinki Bus Co.,Ltd., together with its subsidiaries, provides automobile transportation services in Japan. It operates through Car Transportation, Vehicle Sales and Maintenance, Immovable Properties, Leisure Services, Private Trip, and Others segments. The company offers local and express bus passenger transportation; general chartered bus; mail transportation; automobile driving; vehicle repair; and cleaning and security services for vehicles. It also engages in the sale of automobile parts and tires, as well as crops; insurance agency; land development; building construction; management, brokerage, rental, and sale of real estate properties; operation of food and beverage business, including retail sales at highway kiosks; business management; travel; and transport-related services. In addition, the company is involved in the operation of cableways; sale of food, goods, and cosmetics; advertising agency; web services; nursing care; and childcare activities. The company was formerly known as Shinki Sogo Jidosha K.K. and changed its name to Shinki Bus Co.,Ltd. in 1972. Shinki Bus Co.,Ltd. was incorporated in 1927 and is headquartered in Himeji, Japan."
